subSections.text:
{{ja-noun|かま}}

# a [[sickle]]
#* {{quote-book|||Vol.1
|||date=Feb 4 1999
|publisher={{w|Konami}}
|lang=ja
|chapter={{lj|ダークキラー}}
|trans-chapter=Dark Killer}}
#*: {{ja-usex|'''カマ'''のように発%達した腕を振り回し攻%撃してくる。|'''カマ''' の よう に はっ%たつ した うで を ふりまわし こう%げき してくる。|It attacks with its arms, which have grown like '''sickles'''.}}
# a [[sickle]]-shaped [[weapon]], such as a [[polearm]] with a sickle-shaped blade, or a {{m|ja|鎖鎌|tr=kusarigama}}
#* {{quote-book|||Booster 3
|||date=Jul 5 1999
|publisher={{w|Konami}}
|lang=ja
|chapter={{lj|[音](オト)[女](メ)}}
|trans-chapter=Sonicmaiden}}
#*: {{ja-usex|音を扱うのが得%意なオトメ。音%符の'''カマ'''を使い攻%撃する。|おと を あつかう の が とく%い な オトメ。おん%ぷ の '''カマ''' を つ かい こう%げき する。|A maiden proud of her ability to manipulate sound. She attacks with her musical-note-shaped scythe.}}
# short for {{m|ja|火打鎌|tr=hiuchigama}}: a [[striker]] for lighting [[fire]]s {{qualifier|from the way that pieces of a broken ''kama'' blade were used for this purpose}}
# {{lb|ja|sort=かま|slang}} a [[perverse]] or [[bent]] [[tendency]] or way of [[thinking]] {{qualifier|from the way a ''kama'' blade bends}}
# {{lb|ja|sort=かま|slang}} a [[person]] with a [[perverse]] or [[bent]] [[tendency]] or way of [[thinking]]
# a category of {{m|ja|家紋|tr=kamon||family crest}} featuring a sickle
# {{lb|ja|sort=かま|woodworking}} short for {{m|ja|鎌継ぎ|tr=kamatsugi}}: a [[w:Hammer-headed tenon|hammer-headed tenon]] {{qualifier|from the way the [[sickle]] blade sticks out perpendicular to the handle, similar to the sides of the hammer head on this kind of [[tenon]]}}
# {{lb|ja|sort=かま|slang}} [[excessive]] [[talkativeness]] {{qualifier|probably by sound association with the word {{m|ja|喧しい|tr=yakamashii||noisy}}}}
# {{lb|ja|sort=かま|slang}} an excessively [[talkative]] person
# {{lb|ja|sort=かま|slang}} a [[penis]] {{qualifier|probably from the way that a sickle blade sticks out perpendicular to the handle}}

{{der-top}}
* {{ja-r|鎌%槍|かま%やり}}: a kind of [[polearm]] with a [[sickle]]-shaped [[blade]]
* {{ja-r|大%鎌|おお%がま}}: a [[scythe]]
* {{ja-r|鎖%鎌|くさり%がま}}: a [[sickle]] [[chain]], a kind of [[weapon]]
* {{ja-r|草%刈り鎌|くさ%かりがま}}: a [[sickle]] for [[mow]]ing [[grass]]
{{der-bottom}}

{{der-top|Idioms}}
* {{ja-r|鎌が切れる|かま が きれる}}: “the sickle cuts well” → to do things with authority, to get things sorted quickly and efficiently, to do things crisply and tidily
* {{ja-r|鎌を掛ける|かま を かける}}: “to apply the sickle” → to get something out of a person without them being aware (compare English {{m|en|glean|to glean}}); to [[tempt]] someone, to [[draw]] someone out
* {{ja-r|鎌に掛かる|かま に かかる}}: “to be caught by a sickle” → to be [[take in|taken in]] by someone, to be [[fooled]] or [[tricked]]
{{der-bottom}}
